name: Svalinn Shield
description: Neutralizes "effective against armored" bonuses.

name: Grani's Shield
description: Neutralizes "effective against cavalry" bonuses.

name: Iote's Shield
description: Neutralizes "effective against fliers" bonuses.

name: Close Counter
description: Enables unit to counterattack regardless of distance to attacker.

name: Distant Counter
description: Enables unit to counterattack regardless of distance to attacker.

name: Triangle Adept 1
description: Gives Atk+10% if weapon-triangle advantage, Atk -10% if disadvantage.

name: Triangle Adept 2
description: Gives Atk+15% if weapon-triangle advantage, Atk -15% if disadvantage.

name: Triangle Adept 3
description: Gives Atk +20% if weapon-triangle advantage, Atk -20% if disadvantage.

name: Heavy Blade 1
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Atk \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Atk+5, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Heavy Blade 2
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Atk \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Atk+3, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Heavy Blade 3
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Atk \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Atk, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Flashing Blade 1
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Spd \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Spd+5, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Flashing Blade 2
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Spd \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Spd+3, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Flashing Blade 3
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Spd \xe2\x89\xa5 foe\xe2\x80\x99s Spd, grants Special cooldown charge +1 per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Bonus Doubler 1
description: Grants bonus to Atk/Spd/Def/Res during combat = 50% of current bonus on each of unit\xe2\x80\x99s stats. Calculates each stat bonus independently.

name: Bonus Doubler 2
description: Grants bonus to Atk/Spd/Def/Res during combat = 75% of current bonus on each of unit\xe2\x80\x99s stats. Calculates each stat bonus independently.

name: Bonus Doubler 3
description: Grants bonus to Atk/Spd/Def/Res during combat = current bonus on each of unit\xe2\x80\x99s stats. Calculates each stat bonus independently.

name: Sorcery Blade 1
description: At start of combat, if unit\xe2\x80\x99s HP = 100% and unit is adjacent to a magic ally, calculates damage using the lower of foe\xe2\x80\x99s Def or Res.

name: Sorcery Blade 2
description: At start of combat, if unit\xe2\x80\x99s HP \xe2\x89\xa5 50% and unit is adjacent to a magic ally,  calculates damage using the lower of foe\xe2\x80\x99s Def or Res.

name: Sorcery Blade 3
description: At start of combat, if unit is adjacent to a magic ally,  calculates damage using the lower of foe\xe2\x80\x99s Def or Res.

name: Flashing Blade 4
description: If unit\xe2\x80\x99s Spd > foe\xe2\x80\x99s Spd, grants Special cooldown charge +1 and deals +5 damage per unit\xe2\x80\x99s attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Heavy Blade 4
description: If unit's Atk > foe's Atk, grants Special cooldown charge +1 and deals +5 damage to foe per unit's attack. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack.)

name: Distant Foil
description: If sword, lance, axe, bow, dagger, or beast foe initiates combat, grants Atk/Def+5 to unit during combat and unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range.

name: Close Foil
description: If sword, lance, axe, bow, dagger, or beast foe initiates combat, grants Atk/Def+5 to unit during combat and unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range.

name: Distant Ward
description: If magic, staff, or dragonstone foe initiates combat, grants Atk/Res+5 to unit during combat and unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range.

name: Close Ward
description: If magic, staff, or dragonstone foe initiates combat, unit can counterattack regardless of foe\'s range, disables foe\'s skills that "calculate damage using the lower of foe\'s Def or Res, and grants Atk/Res+5 to unit during combat.

name: Distant Pressure
description: Unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range.  At start of combat, if unit's HP \xe2\x89\xa5 25%, grants Spd+5 during combat, but after combat, if unit attacked, deals 5 damage to unit.

name: Distant Stance
description: Unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range. If foe initiates combat, grants Res+5 to unit during combat.

name: Close Reversal
description: If foe initiates combat, grants Def+5 to unit during combat and unit can counterattack regardless of foe's range.

description: Unit can counterattack regardless of foe\xe2\x80\x99s range. If foe initiates combat, grants Atk/Def +4 during combat.

name: Laws of Sacae II
description: If unit initiates combat or if unit is within 2 spaces of an ally, grants Atk/Spd/Def/Res+6 during combat, and also, if foe uses sword, lance, axe, dragonstone, or beast damage and unit's Spd \xe2\x89\xa5 foe's Spd+5, foe cannot counterattack.

name: Ashera
description: Neutralizes "effective against flying" bonuses. If unit is adjacent to only beast or dragon allies or if unit is not adjacent to any ally, grants Atk/Def+6 during combat.

name: Dragoon Shield
description: Neutralizes "effective against flying" bonuses. Grants Atk/Spd/Def+3.

name: Dragonscale
description: Neutralizes "effective against flying" bonuses. If foe initiates combat or if foe\'s HP = 100% at start of combat, inflicts Atk/Res -6 on foe and grants Special cooldown charge +1 per foe\'s attack during combat. (Only highest value applied. Does not stack. Special coodlown charge granted even if foe\'s attack deals 0 damage.)
